::Aerotaur::
    "I'll be fine, little one.  Don't worry about me."  With his reserves 
down to 50% he shut down the transfer.  He let out a relaxed sigh and reeled 
in his cable.  "There that should be enough energy for now.  And I'm fine 
Trinity."  He stretches out his arms and wings and sits down on the ground.  
"Wow.  Do you have any idea what it's like to not be able to sit at all.  
This feels good."
